title: Mahomes!, Brady Quinn on NFL Week 4 (Football 10/02)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Sean Wagner to break down the MNF game between he Chiefs and Broncos and heap praise on Patrick Mahomes for his comeback victory in Denver. Then Brady Quinn joins the show to talk about the latest action from around the NFL, including the surprising Steelers losing again and much more.
